    {
      "type": "action",
      "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/actions/OneAction.webp",
      "name": "Dread Marshal Stance",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Kordiatra encourages her allies to strike fear into their foes with vicious attacks. When Kordaitra enters this stance, she attempts a @Check[type:intimidation|dc:27] check.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> Kordaitra's marshal's aura increases to a @Template[type:emanation|distance:20], and it grants her and allies a +2 status bonus to damage rolls. When Kordaitra or an ally in the aura critically hits an enemy with a Strike, that enemy is @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Frightened]{Frightened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> As critical success, but Kordaitra's aura size doesn't increase.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> Kordaitra fails to enter the stance.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> Kordaitra fails to enter the stance and can't take this action again for 1 minute.</p>"
        },
